Develop a java program to manage a list of grocery items. Each grocery item should have the following attributes:

Name
Price per unit
Quantity in stock
Stock update date and time ((it changed every time when quantity changes)

Your program should provide the following functionalities:

1. Add a new grocery item to the list.
2. Update the quantity of a grocery item in stock.
3. Display the list of grocery items including their name, prices and quantities.
4. Remove all empty stock items. (quantity in stock is zero).
5. Display all products for which stock updated (quantity changed) in last 3 days.

